    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a great little project. Easy on the wallet and priced to move, it\u2019s a chance to get into a car without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re practical and know how to spot value, come take a look.",
