      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Budget-friendly driver/project with solid bones and a strong-running powertrain. Starts, runs, and moves, with the engine pulling cleanly and the transmission doing its job. Not a show car and it needs cosmetic/mechanical attention, but it\u2019s a straightforward platform for someone who wants an affordable car with usable road manners and good parts value. Great candidate for a daily-beater, weekend project, or drivetrain donor. Priced to sell.",
