    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with tons of personality, this car has the kind of honest, broken-in charm that makes every drive feel like a story in progress. It\u2019s an ideal pick for someone who wants affordable wheels, a capable project, or a dependable runaround with character you just can\u2019t fake. If you appreciate potential and don\u2019t mind a little grit, this one offers a chance to get into a vehicle with real presence at a budget-friendly price.",
      "price": 5900.0,
