      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is being offered as an honest-value opportunity for the right buyer. Best suited for someone seeking affordable transportation, a project car, or a practical option without a premium price tag. Offered as-is and priced to reflect its condition, it represents a straightforward chance to get behind the wheel for less.",
