    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels with some life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runabout that could suit someone needing cheap transport, a first project, or a handy spare vehicle. It has the kind of character that comes with age, and for the right buyer it offers plenty of value for the money. If you want something affordable and straightforward, this could be well worth a look.",
